Here's a fun game to play.  The object of the game is to move the red block
around without getting hit by the blue blocks or touching the black walls. 
 
If you can go longer than 22 seconds you are phenomenal.  I was told that the
Air Force uses this for fighter pilots. They are expected to go for at least
2 minutes. Give it a try!! If you can't get to 22 seconds, stick to driving
golf carts...
 
                                      http://tinyurl.com/56t9u
 
To start, you click on the red block and hold your button down.  You can then
move the block around.
